data.description: This home’s floor plan features a traditional separate formal living & dining rooms with a modern open kitchen and family room. The kitchen has been updated grey cabinets, neutral stone counters, stainless appliances and an oversized farmhouse sink. The fully fenced backyard includes a large deck that’s perfect for entertaining. Oversized primary bedroom with new tub and tile in the ensuite bath and a spacious walk-in closet. Three other bedrooms and a full bath round out the second floor. Down in the basement you'll find the 5th bedroom and 3rd full bath. The rec-room is pre-wired for surround sound, a wet bar with cabinetry and a beverage fridge. There's a water line hooked up for a full size refrigerator. Close proximity to MCB Quantico, i95, commuter lots. A short drive to Barley Naked Brewery, Grounds Bistro, Neighborhood Walmart and more!
